trans-unit.source: Animates from the <xref:System.Double> value of the previous key frame to its own <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.DoubleKeyFrame.Value*> using linear interpolation.
trans-unit.target: Animerer fra den <xref:System.Double>verdien for den forrige key rammen til sin egen <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.DoubleKeyFrame.Value*>ved hjelp av Lineær interpolering.</xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.DoubleKeyFrame.Value*> </xref:System.Double>

trans-unit.source: This class is used as part of a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.DoubleKeyFrameCollection> in conjunction with a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.DoubleAnimationUsingKeyFrames> to animate a <xref:System.Double> property value along a set of key frames.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen brukes som en del av en <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.DoubleKeyFrameCollection>sammen med en <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.DoubleAnimationUsingKeyFrames>å animere en <xref:System.Double>egenskapsverdien langs et sett med nøkkelen for forhandleren.</xref:System.Double> </xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.DoubleAnimationUsingKeyFrames> </xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.DoubleKeyFrameCollection>

trans-unit.source: A key frame defines a segment of the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.DoubleAnimationUsingKeyFrames> to which it belongs.
trans-unit.target: Definerer en nøkkel for en del av den <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.DoubleAnimationUsingKeyFrames>som den tilhører.</xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.DoubleAnimationUsingKeyFrames>

trans-unit.source: Each key frame has a target <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.DoubleKeyFrame.Value%2A> and a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.DoubleKeyFrame.KeyTime%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Hver key ramme har et mål <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.DoubleKeyFrame.Value%2A>og <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.DoubleKeyFrame.KeyTime%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.DoubleKeyFrame.KeyTime%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.DoubleKeyFrame.Value%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.DoubleKeyFrame.KeyTime%2A> specifies the time at which the key frame's <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.DoubleKeyFrame.Value%2A> should be reached.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.DoubleKeyFrame.KeyTime%2A>angir tiden som nøkkelen rammens <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.DoubleKeyFrame.Value%2A>kan nås.</xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.DoubleKeyFrame.Value%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.DoubleKeyFrame.KeyTime%2A>

trans-unit.source: A key frame animates from the target value of the previous key frame to its own target value.
trans-unit.target: En nøkkel ramme animerer fra målverdien tidligere nøkkelen rammens til verdien målet.

trans-unit.source: It starts when the previous key frame ends and ends when its own key time is reached.
trans-unit.target: Starter når den forrige key rammen slutter og slutter når sin egen key time er nådd.

trans-unit.source: Linear key frames like LinearDoubleKeyFrame create a smooth, linear interpolation between values.
trans-unit.target: Lineær nøkkelen forhandleren som LinearDoubleKeyFrame opprette et jevnt, Lineær interpolering mellom verdier.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Animation.LinearDoubleKeyFrame"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Animation.LinearDoubleKeyFrame"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Animation.LinearDoubleKeyFrame"></xref> class with the specified ending value.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Animation.LinearDoubleKeyFrame"> </xref> klasse angitte sluttverdien.

trans-unit.source: Ending value (also known as "target value") for the key frame.
trans-unit.target: SLUTTVERDI (også kjent som "målverdien") for nøkkelen rammen.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Animation.LinearDoubleKeyFrame"></xref> class with the specified ending value and key time.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Animation.LinearDoubleKeyFrame"> </xref> klassen med den angitte verdien og nøkkel sluttidspunktet.

trans-unit.source: Ending value (also known as "target value") for the key frame.
trans-unit.target: SLUTTVERDI (også kjent som "målverdien") for nøkkelen rammen.

trans-unit.source: Key time for the key frame.
trans-unit.target: Key time for nøkkelen rammen.

trans-unit.source: The key time determines when the target value is reached which is also when the key frame ends.
trans-unit.target: Key time bestemmer når målverdien er nådd som er også når key rammens slutter.

trans-unit.source: Creates a new instance of <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Animation.LinearDoubleKeyFrame"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter en ny forekomst av <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Animation.LinearDoubleKeyFrame"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: A new <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Animation.LinearDoubleKeyFrame"></xref> instance.
trans-unit.target: En ny <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Animation.LinearDoubleKeyFrame"> </xref> forekomsten.

trans-unit.source: Interpolates, in a linear fashion, between the previous key frame value and the value of the current key frame, using the supplied progress increment.
trans-unit.target: Interpolerer, en lineær behov mellom forrige nøkkel for verdi og verdi for gjeldende key rammen, ved hjelp av det angitte pågår-intervallet.

trans-unit.source: The value to animate from.
trans-unit.target: Verdien for å animere fra.

trans-unit.source: A value between 0.0 and 1.0, inclusive, that specifies the percentage of time that has elapsed for this key frame.
trans-unit.target: En verdi mellom 0,0 og 1,0 med, som angir prosentdelen av tiden som er utløpt for denne nøkkelen rammen.

trans-unit.source: The output value of this key frame given the specified base value and progress.
trans-unit.target: Output-verdien for denne nøkkelen rammen gitt angitte grunnverdi og pågår.
